headline.main: A Dozen Mariners Set Sail, World Baseball Classic on Deck
headline.print_headline: A Dozen Mariners Set Sail, World Baseball Classic on Deck

lead_paragraph: Robinson Cano, Nelson Cruz and Jean Segura were in a bit of a hurry after playing part of a spring training game over the weekend for the Seattle Mariners.
